review: I recently visited Dr. Vahini's clinic for a check-up and cleaning, and I had a great experience. The staff was super friendly and welcoming from the start and the clinic has a nice calming vibe which made me feel at ease. The team explained everything they were doing and made sure I was comfortable throughout my visit. I appreciated that they took the time to answer all my questions.

Dr.Vahini and team treated a very troubling teeth and gum issue with utmost care, they were very thorough, even with after care. She checked in on me regularly to help with pain management and infections. The clinic itself is very aesthetic and all the staff have very good bedside manner. I highly recommend them also because they bring in specialists to suit the need of the patient.

We have been consulting with Dr.Vahini for over three years now. She’s very friendly and approachable. My kids specially love visiting their fav dentist ( I love the way she handles the kids making them want to go back for follow on checks without throwing tantrums). Glad to have found her

Highly recommend Dr Vahini at The Dental Venue. Been going to her for 16 years and the experience has always been very positive. It is very reassuring to have a dentist who one trusts, the clinic is very well maintained, staff is very well trained and friendly. The quality of care has always been excellent.

Dr. Venkat Reddy and  Dr. Vahini Reddy have been trusted  dentists for our entire family. 
From the convenience of getting an appointment,  effective treatments, good follow ups have made our experience at Dental Avenue seamless. 
Highly recommend Dental Avenue .
I have been visiting her practice for the last 12 years and have always had positive outcomes.From root canals to extractionds to fillings, all the jobs have been done to my satisfaction.
Dr. Vahini’s method  is very practical, thorough & patient . I would highly recommend her as a doctor especially for implant treatment.

Dr reddy explained the process and my extraction got over before I realised. Pain was minimal
Efficient
Friendly
Relaxed experience and expert care by the entire team of doctors. Would recommend The Dental Venue any day.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
